 />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>二次大戰結束幾耐=香港700萬人思維落後左幾耐<br />\n我講完仲比深黃傻粉咬緊</strong>"},{"pid":"5eecc66723898d93f3e2845fd8bdc72e0056abb2","tid":2059460,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"謝謝律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c01adbecc25e575bb2aa36e13fd6b8f9be74a9","tid":2059460,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}